quran[40]{c,v,t}:
  75,1,"M na wẽen ne Yikrã raare."
  75,2,"M na wẽen yεs ne yõor sẽn sãbsd a menga."
  75,3,"Ninsaal tẽedame tɩ Tõnd pa na n tol n tigim a kõbã ye."
  75,4,"Yaa sɩda, Tõnd tõeeme n tigim a nug-bi wã."
  75,5,"Pa woto ye, ninsaal ratame n kell n tong ɑ wẽngrã n pɑ bɑsdẽ ye."
  75,6,"A sokdame: wakat bʋg la Yikrã raare."
  75,7,"Lak tɩ ninã sã n wa nodge."
  75,8,"Tɩ kiuugã sobge."
  75,9,"Tɩ b tigim wĩntoogã ne kiuugã."
  75,10,"Raarã, ninsaal yetame: ""Põsg zĩig bε?"""
  75,11,"Tek woto! Lεbeng zĩig ka be ye."
  75,12,"Lεbeng zĩig yaa fo Soabã nengẽ ra-kãng raare."
  75,13,"B togsda ninsaal ra-kãng raarã a sẽn tʋm tɩ reng taoore, la a sẽn yaoole."
  75,14,"Pa woto ye! Ninsaalã mii a mengã."
  75,15,"Ba t'a wa ne a pademsã."
  75,16,"Ra rãmb f zɩlemdã ne-a (Alkʋrãɑnɑ) n yãgd ne-a ye."
  75,17,"Ad a tigingã (fo sũurã pʋgẽ) la a sẽn karemd to-to wã, roga Tõnd zugu."
  75,18,"Rẽnd ɑ Gibriil sã n karemd-a bɩ f tũneg a kaorengã."
  75,19,"Rẽ poorẽ, ad a vẽnegrã roga Tõnd zugu."
  75,20,"Pa woto ye! Yãmb nonga tʋʋllã (Dũni)."
  75,21,"La y basd yaoolmã (Laahre)."
  75,22,"Nems n be n bʋgs raaren-kãng raarã."
  75,23,"N togl b Soabã n getẽ."
  75,24,"Nems yεs n weoog ra-kãng raarã."
  75,25,"N tẽed tɩ b na n tʋm-b-la lim-limi."
  75,26,"Pa woto ye! A (yõorã) sã n wa ta rɑgsendɑkẽ wã,"
  75,27,"Tɩ b yeele: ""ãnd la tɩpa n sõng-do?"""
  75,28,"T'a bãng n wãag tɩ yaa welgr bala."
  75,29,"Tɩ kars kal tɑɑba(tɩ lebg pɑkre)."
  75,30,"Fo Soabã nengẽ ra-kãng raarã la peeg n tʋg zĩigẽ."
  75,31,"Lɑ ɑ pa kõ sɩda, a ka pʋʋs me."
  75,32,"La bala a yagsame la a gõd a kuidga."
  75,33,"Rẽ poorẽ a kẽnga a nebã nengẽ n gãeesdẽ."
  75,34,"Tall-fo, tɩ sõmba ne-fo."
  75,35,"Rẽ poorẽ tall-fo, sõmba ne-fo."
  75,36,"Ninsaal tẽedame tɩ b na n bas-a-la zaalem bala."
  75,37,"A ra pa yɩ bεrg n yaa mani n raagdẽ."
  75,38,"Rẽ poorẽ n yɩ zɩ-pelle t'A naan-ɑ n kõ-a ra-sãnde?"
  75,39,"T'A naan sẽn tũ ne yẽ pʋgẽ buk a yiibã, raoa la paga."
  75,40,"Rẽ yĩnga Yẽnda pa yɩ n yaa Tõogd n na n vʋʋg kũ-rãmbã?"
